{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"556519-angry-akku","title":"غصیلی اکّو","description":"اکّو کا دن کافی خراب رہا جس کی وجہ سے اُسے بہت، بہت ہی زیادہ غصّہ آیا. اس کتاب کو پڑھیے اور جانیے کہ اس نے اپنے غصّے پر کس طرح قابو پایا. اورساتھ ہی یہ معلومات بھی حاصل کریں کہ جب آپ کو بہت، بہت ہی زیادہ غصّہ آئے تو آپ کو کیا کرنا چاہیے. \r\n\r\n","language":"Urdu","langCode":"ur","isRtl":true,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Khaja Moinoddin  Shaikh "],"illustrators":["Vinayak Varma"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"SCERT, Maharashtra","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/556519-angry-akku"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/724106/size3/155d8763546a35c51598f2685d431da9.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/724106/size6/155d8763546a35c51598f2685d431da9.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/556519/audios/story/556519-angry-akku.mp3","cues":[[1,0,4.44],[2,4.44,4.48],[3,4.48,4.88],[4,4.88,5.4],[5,5.4,5.68],[6,5.68,5.72],[7,5.72,6.84],[8,6.84,7.08],[9,7.08,7.4],[10,7.4,7.84],[11,7.84,8.52],[12,8.52,8.56],[13,8.56,8.88],[14,8.88,8.92],[15,8.92,9.28],[16,9.28,9.36],[17,9.36,9.68],[18,9.68,10.96],[19,10.96,12.2],[20,12.2,12.4],[21,12.4,12.71],[22,12.71,13.12],[23,13.12,13.34],[24,13.34,13.68],[25,13.68,14],[26,14,14.44],[27,14.44,14.86],[28,14.86,15.01],[29,15.01,17.02],[30,17.02,20.34],[31,20.34,20.96],[32,20.96,21.18],[33,21.18,21.56],[34,21.56,22.04],[35,22.04,22.32],[36,22.32,22.5],[37,22.5,22.88],[38,22.88,23.02],[39,23.02,23.38],[40,23.38,23.61],[41,23.61,24.32],[42,24.32,24.84],[43,24.84,25.08],[44,25.08,25.52],[45,25.52,25.84],[46,25.84,26.18],[47,26.18,26.4],[48,26.4,27.11],[49,27.11,27.81],[50,27.81,28.01],[51,28.01,28.41],[52,28.41,29.0